data.description: Nestled along the 10th hole of the Royal Lakes Golf Course, this beautiful home surpasses all expectations. The open concept living area features hardwood floors and an upgraded eat-in kitchen with a breakfast bar. The separate dining room, spacious enough for a 12-person table, adds an elegant touch. On the main floor, two master bedrooms provide luxurious comfort, while the second story boasts an additional bedroom, a bathroom, and an office space or storage space. The finished basement is an entertainer's dream, complete with a fully equipped bar and a beautiful bedroom and full bathroom along with ample amount of storage space . Step outside to the newly painted back porch, which overlooks a fenced-in backyard, adding an extra layer of charm to this paradise-like home. Whether enjoying the golf course views or the well-maintained interiors, this residence is a true gem. The home's prime location offers convenience, being close to shopping, schools, and a local hospital.
